@startuml IngredientOptimizationLogicFlow

title Logic Flow for getHighestScore

start
:Initialize best score to 0;

repeat
  :Iterate over all possible combinations 
  of ingredient amounts //(brute force)//;
  :Calculate capacity, durability, flavor, texture;
  if (Any property < 0?) then (yes)
    :Set property to 0 //(ignore negatives)//;
  endif
  :Calculate score as product of properties;
  :Update best score if current score is higher;
repeat while (More combinations to check?)

:Return best score;

stop

@enduml